How to convert hexadecimal from integer?
print('{:X}'.format(90))
format(90, 'X')

Out:
5A
How to convert octadecimal from integer?
print('{:o}'.format(90))
format(90, 'o')

Out:
132
How to convert binary from integer?
print('{:b}'.format(90))
format(90, 'b')

Out:
1011010


How to padded with zero?
print('{:04X}'.format(90))

Out:
005A
